=head1 DESCRIPTION

The values for a manual Amazon RDS DB cluster snapshot attribute.

=head1 ATTRIBUTES


=head2 AccountIds => ArrayRef[Str|Undef]

The Amazon Web Services account IDs that have access to the manual
Amazon RDS DB cluster snapshot. If the value C<all> is specified, then
the Amazon RDS DB cluster snapshot is public and can be copied or
restored by all Amazon Web Services accounts.

=over

=item *

If the configuration is for an existing Amazon RDS DB cluster snapshot
and you do not specify the C<accountIds> in
C<RdsDbClusterSnapshotAttributeValue>, then the access preview uses the
existing shared C<accountIds> for the snapshot.

=item *

If the access preview is for a new resource and you do not specify the
specify the C<accountIds> in C<RdsDbClusterSnapshotAttributeValue>,
then the access preview considers the snapshot without any attributes.

=item *

To propose deletion of existing shared C<accountIds>, you can specify
an empty list for C<accountIds> in the
C<RdsDbClusterSnapshotAttributeValue>.

=back




